<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3814470>
    dc:description "Figures 21-27. Episinus maculipes Cavanna from Sardinia (21, 23, 24), E. algiricus Lucas from Sardinia (22, 25, 26) and E. theridioides Simon from Corsica (27). Male (21-23, 25), female (24, 26, 27)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3814470/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3814462>
    dc:description "Figures 13-18. Episinus algiricus Lucas (13, 15, 16, 17) from Gallia (MHNP AR 2196) (13, 17) and France: Landes (15, 16; type of E. albescens Denis). E. maculipes Cavanna (14, 18) from Gallia (MHNP AR 2196, sub E. algiricus). Epigynum ventral (13-14), epigynum/vulva, ventral (15, 17-18), dorsal view (16). All figures drawn at same scale. Scale lines: 0.20 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3814462/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3814460>
    dc:description "Figures 10-12. Episinus algiricus Lucas from France, Menton. Male palp, retrolateral (10), ventral (11), prolateral view (12). All figures drawn at same scale. Scale line: 0.30 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3814460/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

